```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(here)
```
Load Data
```{r}
data<- read_csv(here("data", "raw_data", "vp_inh_bo.csv"))
```
```{r}
inh_b<- data %>% ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(
    aes(x = sample,
        y = cq)
  )
```


Save as PNG
```{r}
png(file = here("results","plots", "vp_bo_inh.png"))
inh_b
dev.off()
```
